data.description: Welcome to your dream home located at the end of a cul-de-sac in the stunning Spring Grove Plantation. This exquisite 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of beauty, functionality, and privacy. As you enter, you'll be captivated by the charming curb appeal and the serene surroundings. The well-designed floor plan effortlessly flows from the living room to the kitchen and dining room, creating an inviting space for both relaxation and entertainment. Granite countertops in the kitchen and smooth 9' ceilings throughout. Upstairs, you'll find the luxurious master suite, and two more bedrooms. Additionally, the master suite boasts a wonderful built-in closet ensuring your storage needs are met in style. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning home your own.
